Achievements.Name: CREATOR I
Achievements.Description: CREATE A MALE AND A FEMALE CHARACTER.

Achievements.Name: COULDN'T CARE LESS
Achievements.Description: GET MORE THAN 75 POINTS AT ARCHERY, THEN DESTROY THE SCOREBOARD (PURE MODE, SINGLE PLAYER).

Achievements.Name: CREATOR II
Achievements.Description: CREATE A CUSTOM COMPETITION WITH AT LEAST ONE DISCIPLINE OF EACH SPORT AND WIN IT.

Achievements.Name: BREAKING THE RULES
Achievements.Description: PERFORM A FALSE START, GET A TIMEOUT AND GET DISQUALIFIED IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: SHAKY VICTORY
Achievements.Description: KNOCK OVER FIVE HURDLES IN A 110M HURDLES RACE AND WIN IN SINGLE PLAYER AT MEDIUM DIFFICULTY.

Achievements.Name: EGOIST
Achievements.Description: WIN A TEAM PURSUIT RACE AT CYCLING WITHOUT SWITCHING RIDERS IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: HANGER-ON
Achievements.Description: RUN IN SOMEONE'S SLIPSTREAM FOR TWO MINUTES IN A MIDDLE DISTANCE RACE AND WIN IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: STEADY HAND
Achievements.Description: PERFORM THREE PERFECT GRABS IN ONE RACE AT SWIMMING IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: TURNS OF THE CENTURY
Achievements.Description: PERFORM THREE PERFECT TURNS IN ONE RACE AT SWIMMING IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: PERFECTIONIST II
Achievements.Description: PERFORM A PERFECT RUN-UP AND A PERFECT TAKE OFF IN POLE VAULT IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: PERFECTIONIST I
Achievements.Description: PERFORM A PERFECT START, FLIGHT AND ENTRY WITHIN ONE ATTEMPT AT DIVING IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: BOUNCY VICTORY
Achievements.Description: JUMP OVER ALL HURDLES IN A 110M HURDLES RACE AND WIN IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: PERFECTIONIST III
Achievements.Description: PERFORM THREE PERFECT JUMPS IN A TRIPLE JUMP AND CLEAR 18.20M IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: PERFECTIONIST IV
Achievements.Description: AT HIGH JUMP, RUN UP WITH PERFECT STEPS ONLY AND CLEAR A HEIGHT OF 2.40M IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: PERFECT TIMING
Achievements.Description: THROW WITH PERFECT TIMING IN ALL THROWING EVENTS IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: MARKSMAN
Achievements.Description: WIN A GOLD MEDAL IN ALL ARCHERY AND SKEET SHOOTING EVENTS IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: FLY LIKE AN EAGLE
Achievements.Description: WIN A GOLD MEDAL IN ALL THROWING EVENTS IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: WHEELS OF FORTUNE
Achievements.Description: WIN A GOLD MEDAL IN ALL CYCLING EVENTS IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: DOLPHIN
Achievements.Description: WIN A GOLD MEDAL IN ALL SWIMMING AND DIVING EVENTS IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: CHEETAH
Achievements.Description: WIN A GOLD MEDAL IN ALL RUNNING EVENTS IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: RESPECTABLE COLLECTION
Achievements.Description: COLLECT 15 BRONZE MEDALS IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: SILVER BULLET
Achievements.Description: COLLECT 25 SILVER MEDALS IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: AVERAGE ATHLETE
Achievements.Description: TRAIN FOUR SKILLS TO 50 PERCENT.

Achievements.Name: PROFESSIONAL ATHLETE
Achievements.Description: TRAIN THREE SKILLS TO 75 PERCENT.

Achievements.Name: SPECIALIST
Achievements.Description: MAX OUT A SKILL.

Achievements.Name: GOLDEN HOURS
Achievements.Description: COLLECT 50 GOLD MEDALS IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: CHAMPION
Achievements.Description: WIN THE CAREER.

Achievements.Name: LUCKY STREAK
Achievements.Description: HIT THE BULLSEYE SIX TIMES IN A ROW AT ARCHERY IN SINGLE PLAYER, PURE MODE.

Achievements.Name: ULTIMATE ATHLETE
Achievements.Description: MAXIMIZE ALL OF YOUR SKILLS.

Achievements.Name: DEFYING ALL COMPETITION
Achievements.Description: WIN ALL COMPETITIONS.

Achievements.Name: GENEROUS
Achievements.Description: ALLOW YOUR OPPONENTS A HEAD START OF 5 SECONDS AND WIN IN A SPRINT RACE (RUNNING, SINGLE PLAYER).

Achievements.Name: KANGAROO
Achievements.Description: WIN A GOLD MEDAL IN ALL JUMPING DISCIPLINES IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: ROOKIE
Achievements.Description: ENHANCE TWO SKILLS TO 50 PERCENT.

Achievements.Name: PIGEON HUNTER
Achievements.Description: HIT 15 CLAY PIGEONS IN A ROW IN AN AMERICAN SKEET SHOOTING EVENT IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: DOUBLE AGENT
Achievements.Description: HIT ALL DOUBLES IN AN AMERICAN SKEET SHOOTING EVENT IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: DYNAMIC DUOS
Achievements.Description: HIT ALL DOUBLES AT AN INTERNATIONAL SKEET SHOOTING EVENT IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: STATIONARY SUCCESS
Achievements.Description: HIT ALL CLAY PIGEONS AT STATION FOUR AT AN INTERNATIONAL SKEET SHOOTING EVENT IN SINGLE PLAYER.

Achievements.Name: PATIENT
Achievements.Description: FINISH A SKEET SHOOTING EVENT WITHOUT CALLING 'PULL'.

Achievements.Name: IMPATIENT
Achievements.Description: FINISH A SKEET SHOOTING EVENT CALLING 'PULL' EACH TIME.

Achievements.Name: LEADING ATHLETE
Achievements.Description: PLACE FIRST IN THE HIGHSCORE OF EACH DISCIPLINE (SINGLE PLAYER).

Achievements.Name: TEAM EFFORT
Achievements.Description: LEAD YOUR TEAM TO VICTORY IN THE CO-OP CUP.

Achievements.Name: QUALIFIED ATHLETE
Achievements.Description: FINISH THE BERLIN WORLD CUP QUALIFYING FOR EACH FINAL.

Achievements.Name: HEROES OF BERLIN
Achievements.Description: WIN THE BERLIN WORLD CUP WITH A MALE TEAM.

Achievements.Name: HEROINES OF BERLIN
Achievements.Description: WIN THE BERLIN WORLD CUP WITH A FEMALE TEAM.
